{
  "video_id": "HqekWf-JC-A",
  "title": "Do you really know why you do what you do? | Petter Johansson",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 16360.0,
      "text": "So why do you think the rich should pay more in taxes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16400.0,
      "end_time": 18776.0,
      "text": "Why did you buy the latest iPhone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18800.0,
      "end_time": 21256.0,
      "text": "Why did you pick your current partner?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21280.0,
      "end_time": 24696.0,
      "text": "And why did so many people vote for Donald Trump?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24720.0,
      "end_time": 27240.0,
      "text": "What were the reasons, why did they do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27990.0,
      "end_time": 30950.0,
      "text": "So we ask this kind of question all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30120.0,
      "end_time": 31856.0,
      "text": "and we expect to get an answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31880.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "And when being asked, we expect ourselves to know the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35400.0,
      "end_time": 37519.0,
      "text": "to simply tell why we did as we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38440.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "But do we really know why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41000.0,
      "end_time": 44456.0,
      "text": "So when you say that you prefer George Clooney to Tom Hanks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44479.0,
      "end_time": 46536.0,
      "text": "due to his concern for the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46560.0,
      "end_time": 47760.0,
      "text": "is that really true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48560.0,
      "end_time": 51560.0,
      "text": "So you can be perfectly sincere and genuinely believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51800.0,
      "end_time": 54160.0,
      "text": "that this is the reason that drives your choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 56640.0,
      "text": "but to me, it may still feel like something is missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57560.0,
      "end_time": 60736.0,
      "text": "As it stands, due to the nature of subjectivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60760.0,
      "end_time": 65800.0,
      "text": "it is actually very hard to ever prove that people are wrong about themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66600.0,
      "end_time": 68735.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m an experimental psychologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68760.0,
      "end_time": 72296.0,
      "text": "and this is the problem we&#39;ve been trying to solve in our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72320.0,
      "end_time": 74496.0,
      "text": "So we wanted to create an experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74520.0,
      "end_time": 78560.0,
      "text": "that would allow us to challenge what people say about themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 80760.0,
      "text": "regardless of how certain they may seem."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81960.0,
      "end_time": 84696.0,
      "text": "But tricking people about their own mind is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84720.0,
      "end_time": 87960.0,
      "text": "So we turned to the professionals."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87120.0,
      "end_time": 88320.0,
      "text": "The magicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89120.0,
      "end_time": 92160.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re experts at creating the illusion of a free choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92400.0,
      "end_time": 94336.0,
      "text": "So when they say, \"Pick a card, any card,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94360.0,
      "end_time": 97280.0,
      "text": "the only thing you know is that your choice is no longer free."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98200.0,
      "end_time": 100576.0,
      "text": "So we had a few fantastic brainstorming sessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100600.0,
      "end_time": 102455.0,
      "text": "with a group of Swedish magicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102480.0,
      "end_time": 104122.0,
      "text": "and they helped us create a method"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104147.0,
      "end_time": 108120.0,
      "text": "in which we would be able to manipulate the outcome of people&#39;s choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108760.0,
      "end_time": 111696.0,
      "text": "This way we would know when people are wrong about themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111720.0,
      "end_time": 113760.0,
      "text": "even if they don&#39;t know this themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114480.0,
      "end_time": 119136.0,
      "text": "So I will now show you a short movie showing this manipulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 120576.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s quite simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120600.0,
      "end_time": 122735.0,
      "text": "The participants make a choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122760.0,
      "end_time": 125160.0,
      "text": "but I end up giving them the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125400.0,
      "end_time": 128560.0,
      "text": "And then we want to see: How did they react, and what did they say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132400.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s quite simple, but see if you can spot the magic going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133440.0,
      "end_time": 136960.0,
      "text": "And this was shot with real participants, they don&#39;t know what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 141216.0,
      "text": "(Video) Petter Johansson: Hi, my name&#39;s Petter."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141240.0,
      "end_time": 142455.0,
      "text": "Woman: Hi, I&#39;m Becka."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142479.0,
      "end_time": 144616.0,
      "text": "PJ: I&#39;m going to show you pictures like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144640.0,
      "end_time": 147535.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;ll have to decide which one you find more attractive."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147560.0,
      "end_time": 148776.0,
      "text": "Becka: OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148800.0,
      "end_time": 151976.0,
      "text": "PJ: And then sometimes, I will ask you why you prefer that face."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152000.0,
      "end_time": 153216.0,
      "text": "Becka: OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153240.0,
      "end_time": 154440.0,
      "text": "PJ: Ready? Becka: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163120.0,
      "end_time": 164936.0,
      "text": "PJ: Why did you prefer that one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164960.0,
      "end_time": 166456.0,
      "text": "Becka: The smile, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 166480.0,
      "end_time": 167679.0,
      "text": "PJ: Smile."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172400.0,
      "end_time": 173640.0,
      "text": "Man: One on the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177520.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "Again, this one just struck me."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179760.0,
      "end_time": 181376.0,
      "text": "Interesting shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181400.0,
      "end_time": 184400.0,
      "text": "Since I&#39;m a photographer, I like the way it&#39;s lit and looks."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186280.0,
      "end_time": 188320.0,
      "text": "Petter Johansson: But now comes the trick."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190120.0,
      "end_time": 191400.0,
      "text": "(Video) Woman 1: This one."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196240.0,
      "end_time": 198520.0,
      "text": "PJ: So they get the opposite of their choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 200520.0,
      "end_time": 202120.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s see what happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 208240.0,
      "end_time": 209440.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: Um ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215760.0,
      "end_time": 218560.0,
      "text": "I think he seems a little more innocent than the other guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 225360.0,
      "end_time": 226600.0,
      "text": "Man: The one on the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229280.0,
      "end_time": 232976.0,
      "text": "I like her smile and contour of the nose and face."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233000.0,
      "end_time": 235760.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a little more interesting to me, and her haircut."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 240400.0,
      "end_time": 241239.0,
      "text": "Woman 3: This one."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 243520.0,
      "end_time": 245960.0,
      "text": "I like the smirky look better."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 245120.0,
      "end_time": 247120.0,
      "text": "PJ: You like the smirky look better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 249680.0,
      "end_time": 252856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252880.0,
      "end_time": 254790.0,
      "text": "Woman 3: This one."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255280.0,
      "end_time": 256680.0,
      "text": "PJ: What made you choose him?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257519.0,
      "end_time": 260416.0,
      "text": "Woman 3: I don&#39;t know, he looks a little bit like the Hobbit."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 260440.0,
      "end_time": 262496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 262520.0,
      "end_time": 264150.0,
      "text": "PJ: And what happens in the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 264400.0,
      "end_time": 267136.0,
      "text": "when I tell them the true nature of the experiment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 269616.0,
      "text": "Yeah, that&#39;s it. I just have to ask a few questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 269640.0,
      "end_time": 270856.0,
      "text": "Man: Sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270880.0,
      "end_time": 273856.0,
      "text": "PJ: What did you think of this experiment, was it easy or hard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273880.0,
      "end_time": 275120.0,
      "text": "Man: It was easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276400.0,
      "end_time": 277376.0,
      "text": "PJ: During the experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277400.0,
      "end_time": 280736.0,
      "text": "I actually switched the pictures three times."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 280760.0,
      "end_time": 282336.0,
      "text": "Was this anything you noticed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282360.0,
      "end_time": 284176.0,
      "text": "Man: No. I didn&#39;t notice any of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284200.0,
      "end_time": 285695.0,
      "text": "PJ: Not at all? Man: No."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 285720.0,
      "end_time": 287816.0,
      "text": "Switching the pictures as far as ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287840.0,
      "end_time": 291655.0,
      "text": "PJ: Yeah, you were pointing at one of them but I actually gave you the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 291680.0,
      "end_time": 293496.0,
      "text": "Man: The opposite one. OK, when you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293520.0,
      "end_time": 295775.0,
      "text": "No. Shows you how much my attention span was."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 295800.0,
      "end_time": 297320.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 298880.0,
      "end_time": 301896.0,
      "text": "PJ: Did you notice that sometimes during the experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 301920.0,
      "end_time": 304560.0,
      "text": "I switched the pictures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 306960.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: No, I did not notice that."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306120.0,
      "end_time": 309120.0,
      "text": "PJ: You were pointing at one, but then I gave you the other one."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 309920.0,
      "end_time": 311536.0,
      "text": "No inclination of that happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311560.0,
      "end_time": 313136.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: No."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313160.0,
      "end_time": 314416.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: I did not notice."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 314440.0,
      "end_time": 316376.0,
      "text": "(Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316400.0,
      "end_time": 317616.0,
      "text": "PJ: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317640.0,
      "end_time": 319150.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 319400.0,
      "end_time": 321960.0,
      "text": "PJ: OK, so as you probably figured out now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 321120.0,
      "end_time": 323376.0,
      "text": "the trick is that I have two cards in each hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323400.0,
      "end_time": 324976.0,
      "text": "and when I hand one of them over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 325000.0,
      "end_time": 329360.0,
      "text": "the black one kind of disappears into the black surface on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 330640.0,
      "end_time": 332376.0,
      "text": "So using pictures like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 332400.0,
      "end_time": 336775.0,
      "text": "normally not more than 20 percent of the participants detect these tries."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336800.0,
      "end_time": 338216.0,
      "text": "And as you saw in the movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338240.0,
      "end_time": 341416.0,
      "text": "when in the end we explain what&#39;s going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341440.0,
      "end_time": 345816.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re very surprised and often refuse to believe the trick has been made."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 345840.0,
      "end_time": 350616.0,
      "text": "So this shows that this effect is quite robust and a genuine effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 350640.0,
      "end_time": 353296.0,
      "text": "But if you&#39;re interested in self-knowledge, as I am,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 353320.0,
      "end_time": 354656.0,
      "text": "the more interesting bit is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354680.0,
      "end_time": 358616.0,
      "text": "OK, so what did they say when they explained these choices?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 358640.0,
      "end_time": 360135.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve done a lot of analysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 360160.0,
      "end_time": 362240.0,
      "text": "of the verbal reports in these experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 363360.0,
      "end_time": 365816.0,
      "text": "And this graph simply shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 365840.0,
      "end_time": 370616.0,
      "text": "that if you compare what they say in a manipulated trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 370640.0,
      "end_time": 372150.0,
      "text": "with a nonmanipulated trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 372400.0,
      "end_time": 374816.0,
      "text": "that is when they explain a normal choice they&#39;ve made"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374840.0,
      "end_time": 377335.0,
      "text": "and one where we manipulated the outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377360.0,
      "end_time": 379816.0,
      "text": "we find that they are remarkably similar."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 379840.0,
      "end_time": 382895.0,
      "text": "So they are just as emotional, just as specific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 382920.0,
      "end_time": 386120.0,
      "text": "and they are expressed with the same level of certainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387120.0,
      "end_time": 389456.0,
      "text": "So the strong conclusion to draw from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 389480.0,
      "end_time": 391696.0,
      "text": "is that if there are no differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 391720.0,
      "end_time": 395416.0,
      "text": "between a real choice and a manipulated choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 395440.0,
      "end_time": 397880.0,
      "text": "perhaps we make things up all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 398680.0,
      "end_time": 400160.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve also done studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 400400.0,
      "end_time": 403560.0,
      "text": "where we try to match what they say with the actual faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 403800.0,
      "end_time": 404960.0,
      "text": "And then we find things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405760.0,
      "end_time": 410816.0,
      "text": "So here, this male participant, he preferred the girl to the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 410840.0,
      "end_time": 412695.0,
      "text": "he ended up with the one to the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 412720.0,
      "end_time": 415536.0,
      "text": "And then, he explained his choice like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 415560.0,
      "end_time": 416856.0,
      "text": "\"She is radiant."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 416880.0,
      "end_time": 419976.0,
      "text": "I would rather have approached her at the bar than the other one."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 420000.0,
      "end_time": 421616.0,
      "text": "And I like earrings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421640.0,
      "end_time": 425135.0,
      "text": "And whatever made him choose the girl on the left to begin with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 425160.0,
      "end_time": 426736.0,
      "text": "it can&#39;t have been the earrings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 426760.0,
      "end_time": 429616.0,
      "text": "because they were actually sitting on the girl on the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 429640.0,
      "end_time": 433416.0,
      "text": "So this is a clear example of a post hoc construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 433440.0,
      "end_time": 436240.0,
      "text": "So they just explained the choice afterwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 437320.0,
      "end_time": 439616.0,
      "text": "So what this experiment shows is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 439640.0,
      "end_time": 443296.0,
      "text": "OK, so if we fail to detect that our choices have been changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 443320.0,
      "end_time": 446520.0,
      "text": "we will immediately start to explain them in another way."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 447520.0,
      "end_time": 448775.0,
      "text": "And what we also found"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 448800.0,
      "end_time": 452160.0,
      "text": "is that the participants often come to prefer the alternative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 452400.0,
      "end_time": 454296.0,
      "text": "that they were led to believe they liked."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 454320.0,
      "end_time": 456336.0,
      "text": "So if we let them do the choice again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 456360.0,
      "end_time": 460120.0,
      "text": "they will now choose the face they had previously rejected."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 461520.0,
      "end_time": 463816.0,
      "text": "So this is the effect we call \"choice blindness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 463840.0,
      "end_time": 466560.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve done a number of different studies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 466800.0,
      "end_time": 468616.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve tried consumer choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 468640.0,
      "end_time": 473560.0,
      "text": "choices based on taste and smell and even reasoning problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 473800.0,
      "end_time": 475135.0,
      "text": "But what you all want to know is of course"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 475160.0,
      "end_time": 479960.0,
      "text": "does this extend also to more complex, more meaningful choices?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 479120.0,
      "end_time": 482200.0,
      "text": "Like those concerning moral and political issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 484400.0,
      "end_time": 488616.0,
      "text": "So the next experiment, it needs a little bit of a background."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 488640.0,
      "end_time": 492895.0,
      "text": "So in Sweden, the political landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492920.0,
      "end_time": 496280.0,
      "text": "is dominated by a left-wing and a right-wing coalition."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497720.0,
      "end_time": 502136.0,
      "text": "And the voters may move a little bit between the parties within each coalition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 502160.0,
      "end_time": 504920.0,
      "text": "but there is very little movement between the coalitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 505680.0,
      "end_time": 507656.0,
      "text": "And before each elections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 507680.0,
      "end_time": 511896.0,
      "text": "the newspapers and the polling institutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 511920.0,
      "end_time": 514536.0,
      "text": "put together what they call \"an election compass\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 514558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517894.99999999994,
      "text": "which consists of a number of dividing issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 517919.0,
      "end_time": 520256.0,
      "text": "that sort of separates the two coalitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 520280.0,
      "end_time": 524150.0,
      "text": "Things like if tax on gasoline should be increased"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 524390.0,
      "end_time": 528135.0,
      "text": "or if the 13 months of paid parental leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528159.0,
      "end_time": 530655.0,
      "text": "should be split equally between the two parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530679.0,
      "end_time": 533400.0,
      "text": "in order to increase gender equality."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 534840.0,
      "end_time": 537560.0,
      "text": "So, before the last Swedish election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 537800.0,
      "end_time": 539680.0,
      "text": "we created an election compass of our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 540480.0,
      "end_time": 542616.0,
      "text": "So we walked up to people in the street"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 542640.0,
      "end_time": 545976.0,
      "text": "and asked if they wanted to do a quick political survey."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 546000.0,
      "end_time": 548456.0,
      "text": "So first we had them state their voting intention"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 548480.0,
      "end_time": 549840.0,
      "text": "between the two coalitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 550560.0,
      "end_time": 554335.0,
      "text": "Then we asked them to answer 12 of these questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 554360.0,
      "end_time": 556336.0,
      "text": "They would fill in their answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 556360.0,
      "end_time": 557976.0,
      "text": "and we would ask them to discuss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 558000.0,
      "end_time": 563496.0,
      "text": "so OK, why do you think tax on gas should be increased?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 563520.0,
      "end_time": 565616.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;d go through the questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 565640.0,
      "end_time": 569536.0,
      "text": "Then we had a color coded template"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 569560.0,
      "end_time": 572496.0,
      "text": "that would allow us to tally their overall score."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 572520.0,
      "end_time": 575976.0,
      "text": "So this person would have one, two, three, four"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 576000.0,
      "end_time": 579296.0,
      "text": "five, six, seven, eight, nine scores to the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 579320.0,
      "end_time": 582000.0,
      "text": "so he would lean to the left, basically."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 582800.0,
      "end_time": 587240.0,
      "text": "And in the end, we also had them fill in their voting intention once more."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 588160.0,
      "end_time": 590439.0,
      "text": "But of course, there was also a trick involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 591360.0,
      "end_time": 593536.0,
      "text": "So first, we walked up to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 593560.0,
      "end_time": 595616.0,
      "text": "we asked them about their voting intention"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 595640.0,
      "end_time": 597896.0,
      "text": "and then when they started filling in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 597920.0,
      "end_time": 603376.0,
      "text": "we would fill in a set of answers going in the opposite direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 603400.0,
      "end_time": 605976.0,
      "text": "We would put it under the notepad."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606000.0,
      "end_time": 608776.0,
      "text": "And when we get the questionnaire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 608800.0,
      "end_time": 612120.0,
      "text": "we would simply glue it on top of the participant&#39;s own answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 616000.0,
      "end_time": 617240.0,
      "text": "So there, it&#39;s gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 624280.0,
      "end_time": 626656.0,
      "text": "And then we would ask about each of the questions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 626680.0,
      "end_time": 628215.0,
      "text": "How did you reason here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 628240.0,
      "end_time": 629976.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;ll state the reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 630000.0,
      "end_time": 632480.0,
      "text": "together we will sum up their overall score."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634800.0,
      "end_time": 638479.0,
      "text": "And in the end, they will state their voting intention again."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 641960.0,
      "end_time": 643616.0,
      "text": "So what we find first of all here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 643640.0,
      "end_time": 647856.0,
      "text": "is that very few of these manipulations are detected."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 647880.0,
      "end_time": 650536.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re not detected in the sense that they realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 650560.0,
      "end_time": 652415.0,
      "text": "\"OK, you must have changed my answer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 652440.0,
      "end_time": 653696.0,
      "text": "it was more the case that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 653720.0,
      "end_time": 656896.0,
      "text": "\"OK, I must&#39;ve misunderstood the question the first time I read it."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 656920.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "Can I please change it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 659800.0,
      "end_time": 664216.0,
      "text": "And even if a few of these manipulations were changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 664240.0,
      "end_time": 666376.0,
      "text": "the overall majority was missed."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 666400.0,
      "end_time": 670550.0,
      "text": "So we managed to switch 90 percent of the participants&#39; answers"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 670800.0,
      "end_time": 673240.0,
      "text": "from left to right, right to left, their overall profile."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 674800.0,
      "end_time": 679199.0,
      "text": "And what happens then when they are asked to motivate their choices?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 680160.0,
      "end_time": 683216.0,
      "text": "And here we find much more interesting verbal reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 683240.0,
      "end_time": 685256.0,
      "text": "than compared to the faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 685280.0,
      "end_time": 688640.0,
      "text": "People say things like this, and I&#39;ll read it to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 689720.0,
      "end_time": 693456.0,
      "text": "So, \"Large-scale governmental surveillance of email and internet traffic"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 693480.0,
      "end_time": 697816.0,
      "text": "ought to be permissible as means to combat international crime and terrorism.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 697840.0,
      "end_time": 700556.0,
      "text": "\"So you agree to some extent with this statement.\" \"Yes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 700580.0,
      "end_time": 702800.0,
      "text": "\"So how did you reason here?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 703600.0,
      "end_time": 708536.0,
      "text": "\"Well, like, as it is so hard to get at international crime and terrorism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 708560.0,
      "end_time": 711335.0,
      "text": "I think there should be those kinds of tools.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 711360.0,
      "end_time": 714976.0,
      "text": "And then the person remembers an argument from the newspaper in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 715000.0,
      "end_time": 716616.0,
      "text": "\"Like in the newspaper today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 716640.0,
      "end_time": 720160.0,
      "text": "it said they can like, listen to mobile phones from prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 720400.0,
      "end_time": 723575.0,
      "text": "if a gang leader tries to continue his crimes from inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 723600.0,
      "end_time": 726416.0,
      "text": "And I think it&#39;s madness that we have so little power"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 726440.0,
      "end_time": 728960.0,
      "text": "that we can&#39;t stop those things"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 728120.0,
      "end_time": 731560.0,
      "text": "when we actually have the possibility to do so.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 731800.0,
      "end_time": 733776.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s a little bit back and forth in the end:"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 733800.0,
      "end_time": 736376.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t like that they have access to everything I do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 736400.0,
      "end_time": 738976.0,
      "text": "but I still think it&#39;s worth it in the long run.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 739000.0,
      "end_time": 741536.0,
      "text": "So, if you didn&#39;t know that this person"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 741560.0,
      "end_time": 743815.0,
      "text": "just took part in a choice blindness experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 743840.0,
      "end_time": 745696.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think you would question"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 745720.0,
      "end_time": 748840.0,
      "text": "that this is the true attitude of that person."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 749800.0,
      "end_time": 752656.0,
      "text": "And what happens in the end, with the voting intention?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752680.0,
      "end_time": 757376.0,
      "text": "What we find -- that one is also clearly affected by the questionnaire."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 757400.0,
      "end_time": 759136.0,
      "text": "So we have 10 participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 759160.0,
      "end_time": 762136.0,
      "text": "shifting from left to right or from right to left."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 762160.0,
      "end_time": 764695.0,
      "text": "We have another 19 that go from clear voting intention"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 764720.0,
      "end_time": 766176.0,
      "text": "to being uncertain."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 766200.0,
      "end_time": 769296.0,
      "text": "Some go from being uncertain to clear voting intention."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 769320.0,
      "end_time": 774560.0,
      "text": "And then there is a number of participants staying uncertain throughout."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 774800.0,
      "end_time": 775656.0,
      "text": "And that number is interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 775680.0,
      "end_time": 780295.0,
      "text": "because if you look at what the polling institutes say"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 780320.0,
      "end_time": 781976.0,
      "text": "the closer you get to an election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 782000.0,
      "end_time": 784136.0,
      "text": "the only people that are sort of in play"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 784160.0,
      "end_time": 786815.0,
      "text": "are the ones that are considered uncertain."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 786840.0,
      "end_time": 790560.0,
      "text": "But we show there is a much larger number"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 790800.0,
      "end_time": 792880.0,
      "text": "that would actually consider shifting their attitudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 793640.0,
      "end_time": 797136.0,
      "text": "And here I must point out, of course, that you are not allowed to use this"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 797160.0,
      "end_time": 799776.0,
      "text": "as an actual method to change people&#39;s votes"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 799800.0,
      "end_time": 801295.0,
      "text": "before an election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 801320.0,
      "end_time": 804936.0,
      "text": "and we clearly debriefed them afterwards"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 804960.0,
      "end_time": 807256.0,
      "text": "and gave them every opportunity to change back"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 807280.0,
      "end_time": 809760.0,
      "text": "to whatever they thought first."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 810600.0,
      "end_time": 812936.0,
      "text": "But what this shows is that if you can get people"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 812960.0,
      "end_time": 818496.0,
      "text": "to see the opposite view and engage in a conversation with themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 818520.0,
      "end_time": 821439.0,
      "text": "that could actually make them change their views."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 822400.0,
      "end_time": 823600.0,
      "text": "OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 824760.0,
      "end_time": 826415.0,
      "text": "So what does it all mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 826440.0,
      "end_time": 828856.0,
      "text": "What do I think is going on here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 828880.0,
      "end_time": 830960.0,
      "text": "So first of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 830120.0,
      "end_time": 834976.0,
      "text": "a lot of what we call self-knowledge is actually self-interpretation."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 835000.0,
      "end_time": 837496.0,
      "text": "So I see myself make a choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 837520.0,
      "end_time": 840295.0,
      "text": "and then when I&#39;m asked why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 840320.0,
      "end_time": 842856.0,
      "text": "I just try to make as much sense of it as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 842880.0,
      "end_time": 844816.0,
      "text": "when I make an explanation."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 844840.0,
      "end_time": 847856.0,
      "text": "But we do this so quickly and with such ease"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 847880.0,
      "end_time": 852160.0,
      "text": "that we think we actually know the answer when we answer why."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 853400.0,
      "end_time": 856136.0,
      "text": "And as it is an interpretation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 856160.0,
      "end_time": 858456.0,
      "text": "of course we sometimes make mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 858480.0,
      "end_time": 862000.0,
      "text": "The same way we make mistakes when we try to understand other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 863160.0,
      "end_time": 866856.0,
      "text": "So beware when you ask people the question \"why\""
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 866880.0,
      "end_time": 871776.0,
      "text": "because what may happen is that, if you asked them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 871800.0,
      "end_time": 875815.0,
      "text": "\"So why do you support this issue?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 875840.0,
      "end_time": 879560.0,
      "text": "\"Why do you stay in this job or this relationship?\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 879800.0,
      "end_time": 882496.0,
      "text": "what may happen when you ask why is that you actually create an attitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 882520.0,
      "end_time": 884760.0,
      "text": "that wasn&#39;t there before you asked the question."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 885440.0,
      "end_time": 888616.0,
      "text": "And this is of course important in your professional life, as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 888640.0,
      "end_time": 889856.0,
      "text": "or it could be."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 889880.0,
      "end_time": 892415.0,
      "text": "If, say, you design something and then you ask people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 892440.0,
      "end_time": 894696.0,
      "text": "\"Why do you think this is good or bad?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 894720.0,
      "end_time": 897776.0,
      "text": "Or if you&#39;re a journalist asking a politician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 897800.0,
      "end_time": 900175.0,
      "text": "\"So, why did you make this decision?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 900200.0,
      "end_time": 902136.0,
      "text": "Or if indeed you are a politician"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 902160.0,
      "end_time": 904800.0,
      "text": "and try to explain why a certain decision was made."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 906800.0,
      "end_time": 909656.0,
      "text": "So this may all seem a bit disturbing."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 909680.0,
      "end_time": 913175.0,
      "text": "But if you want to look at it from a positive direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 913200.0,
      "end_time": 914936.0,
      "text": "it could be seen as showing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 914960.0,
      "end_time": 918336.0,
      "text": "OK, so we&#39;re actually a little bit more flexible than we think."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 918360.0,
      "end_time": 920256.0,
      "text": "We can change our minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 920280.0,
      "end_time": 922736.0,
      "text": "Our attitudes are not set in stone."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 922760.0,
      "end_time": 925936.0,
      "text": "And we can also change the minds of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 925960.0,
      "end_time": 928336.0,
      "text": "if we can only get them to engage with the issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 928360.0,
      "end_time": 930400.0,
      "text": "and see it from the opposite view."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 931400.0,
      "end_time": 935336.0,
      "text": "And in my own personal life, since starting with this research --"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 935360.0,
      "end_time": 937936.0,
      "text": "So my partner and I, we&#39;ve always had the rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 937960.0,
      "end_time": 940256.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re allowed to take things back."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 940280.0,
      "end_time": 942616.0,
      "text": "Just because I said I liked something a year ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 942640.0,
      "end_time": 944680.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean I have to like it still."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 945480.0,
      "end_time": 948296.0,
      "text": "And getting rid of the need to stay consistent"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 948320.0,
      "end_time": 952680.0,
      "text": "is actually a huge relief and makes relational life so mush easier to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 953720.0,
      "end_time": 956800.0,
      "text": "Anyway, so the conclusion must be:"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 957320.0,
      "end_time": 959816.0,
      "text": "know that you don&#39;t know yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 959840.0,
      "end_time": 962160.0,
      "text": "Or at least not as well as you think you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 963480.0,
      "end_time": 964696.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 964720.0,
      "end_time": 969360.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}